operty></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name Namespace="Tc2_System">GETCPUCOUNTER</Name><Comment><![CDATA[	The CPU cycle counter can be read with this function block. 
	The numerical value is a relative 64 bit integer, which, independently of the CPUs internal clock rate, is output in a form converted into 100ns ticks. 
